programme.desc: Two Hong Kong urban love stories depicting two Hong Kong policemen, both jilted by ex-lovers and falling in love again.

programme.desc: As the police sets to arrest a drug lord, a team of masked thugs steals the drugs. Inspector Bong discovers that the killers are led by Ngo, a former fellow cop who was forced into a life of crime by him.

programme.title: Distinction
programme.desc: Ms Tsui is a music teacher. Zoey is an underachiever. Ka Ho is a rebellious teenager. These three individuals take part in a musical that they deem worthless, but turns out to be a journey of self-discovery.

programme.title: Lion Rock
programme.desc: David Ki, one of the top rock climbers in Asia, lost everything when a motorcycle accident took away his ability to walk. Rather than succumbing to his fate, David found his own way of scaling the dizzying peaks again.

programme.title: A Cool Fish
programme.desc: In this dark-comedy, cop-turned-security guard Ma faces the ultimate challenge when his boss mysteriously disappears and his paralyzed sister makes a morbid deal with the armed bandits who abduct her.

programme.title: Think Big Big
programme.desc: Moon is a plus-sized girl working happily as a mascot at a theme park. That is until one day she accidentally joins a weight loss competition, with her remarkable transformation turning her into the 'Nation's Goddess'.

programme.title: American Girl

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong.

programme.title: Reborn
programme.desc: Programmer and gamer Hao Ming gets approached by mercenary Fei Qiao and businessman Takeshi, and is drawn into a shady hacking game in Malaysia. The cyber mission quickly turns dangerous.

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: An urban sketcher suffering from ALS wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. Then, he asks his old classmate to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day.

programme.title: Bodyguards And Assassins
programme.desc: Chinese revolutionary leader Sun Yat-sen returned to Hong Kong for further plans of overthrowing the Qing Dynasty. Businessman Li and Chan found 4 bodyguards to protect Mr Sun for the assassination of the Qing Dynasty.

programme.title: Mr. & Mrs. Gambler
programme.desc: Manfred and Flora are degenerate gamblers who can gamble on anything. On one fateful day, they both suffer heavy losses and are held hostage by the loan sharks in Macau only to find themselves falling in love.

programme.title: Lost Love
programme.desc: Mei tries to get over the death of her young son by becoming a foster parent. For 13 years, Mei's dedication to the foster child leads her to neglect her husband and the true needs of the child.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 1

programme.title: Love Is Pyjamas
programme.desc: Underwear designer Spring and her daughter work at Hugo's enterprise. Hugo demands a new fashion line design competition between Spring and the newly employed ex model Jojo to save his company from bankruptcy.

programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh.
